Phase 1: Paper Trading (3 Months)
Goal: Validate strategy without risking capital

Daily Routine:
1. Pre-market preparation (15 min)
   - Check economic calendar for gold-related news
   - Note key S/R levels from higher timeframes
   - Record expected volatility (ATR)

2. Trading session (active monitoring)
   - Log every signal (even if not taken)
   - Take screenshots of entries/exits
   - Record execution quality (slippage, fills)

3. End-of-day review (30 min)
   - Update trading journal
   - Calculate daily P&L
   - Note strategy adjustments needed
