Final Professional Advice:
The first 3 months are for learning, not earning

If the paper trading period is profitable (>5%), proceed to forward test

If forward test is profitable (>10% with <10% DD), consider full deployment

Document EVERYTHING - your future self will thank you

The market will humble you - stay disciplined
